snippet.textDisplay: Beautifully done. I am so glad we are seeing all these new artists this season. Living in Southern California, I miss the live concerts I enjoyed back home in Lahore. The only window left for the diaspora is through youtube and Coke Studio. Its a pity we don't get many Pakistani artists performing live here in California. But now I know about Rehma. I got to check out her other work and will definitely would go see her live in LA whenever she does a live show!
